snippet.title: TRAVEL VLOG IV
snippet.description:
Travel and food videos is what you'll find on this channel. Hi! My name's Ivana, but you can call me Iv.  For more than 3 years I've been traveling and eating delicious local food around the world. My travel channel was created for you to be able to travel with me and introduce you to some amazing food. It's such a joy getting comments everyday of people who've also decided to travel as well. Trust me the food is all worth it!

Travel in India is something you can specifically find a lot of information of on this travel channel. India is my favourite country in the world. Also it won't be a surprise I absolutely adore Indian food. India is a phenomenal country and I simply can't get enough of travel here.  If you're planning on taking a trip to India I hope this channel helps you to plan for it.
